AGO V3 - Installation Notes

1 - Copy system/application/config/config.php_template to system/application/config/config.php
2 - Configure config.php to the local configuration
3 - Copy system/application/config/database.php_template to system/application/config/database.php
4 - Configure database.php to the local configuration
5 - Create .htaccess in the root dir (the same of this file) with add the following lines:

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On
    RewriteBase /
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-f
    RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
    RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.php/$1 [L]
</IfModule>

<IfModule !mod_rewrite.c>
    ErrorDocument 404 /index.php
</IfModule>

